      <tr>
        <th>DNS</th>
        <td><code>169.254.169.254</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Gateway</th>
        <td>Enter the first <code>.1</code> address from the CIDR. For example, if the CIDR is <code>192.168.16.0/22</code>, enter <code>192.168.16.1</code>.</td>
